          -  Parent/guardian conversant in English or Spanish

          -  Patient aged 2-18 years

        Exclusion Criteria (For Adolescent):

        • Parent-reported cognitive issues preventing completion of the form, such as in-school
        aide&gt;50% of the school day; special education classes &gt;50% of school day
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
